UI
--------------------------------------------------

Always use

Shadcn/UI

TailwindCSS

Lucide Icons

Responsive by default.

Desktop-first is forbidden.

Mobile-first only.

--------------------------------------------------
FORMS
--------------------------------------------------

Always use

React Hook Form

with

Zod

