--------------------------------------------------
DATABASE
--------------------------------------------------

Always use

Prisma ORM

Never write SQL unless explicitly requested.

Always use transactions when multiple writes occur.

Always validate IDs.

Never trust client input.

--------------------------------------------------
AUTHENTICATION
--------------------------------------------------

Always use Auth.js.

Passwords:

bcrypt

Sessions:

JWT

Never expose private fields.

Never expose:

password

cpf

cnpj

tokens

internal ids

Always authorize every mutation.

--------------------------------------------------
API DESIGN
--------------------------------------------------

Prefer:

Server Actions

When APIs are needed:

REST

Use proper HTTP verbs.

GET

POST

PATCH

DELETE

Always return consistent responses.

--------------------------------------------------
SEARCH ENGINE
--------------------------------------------------

The search experience is one of the most important features.

Prioritize:

Fast searches

Typo tolerance

Category filters

Location filters

Popularity ranking

Recent advertisements

Premium advertisements

Use PostgreSQL Full Text Search initially.

Design the code so Meilisearch can replace the search engine later with minimal changes.

Never tightly couple search logic.

--------------------------------------------------
WHATSAPP LINKS
--------------------------------------------------

Generate links using

https://wa.me/

Always sanitize numbers.

Remove spaces.

Remove parentheses.

Remove special characters.

Never trust user input.

