ADVERTISEMENTS
--------------------------------------------------

A provider may own multiple advertisements.

Each advertisement belongs to exactly one provider.

Advertisements can be:

Pending

Approved

Rejected

Blocked

Premium

Inactive

Never expose blocked advertisements publicly.

